        <span id="score-left" class="w-[85%] transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out cursor-pointer p-10 text-5xl font-extrabold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-500 via-red-500 to-orange-400  rounded-xl border-4 border-white shadow-lg text-center tracking-wide select-none">0</span>
